<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MOZCOMPRAS - Sua loja de infoprodutos</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .hero {
            padding: 8rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            color: white;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 3rem;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #6366f1;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            background: #f8fafc;
        }

        .features {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: -4rem auto 4rem;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Modal Styles */
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 50;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 500px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }

        .close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1.25rem;
            right: 1.25rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .registration-form h2 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .registration-form p.info {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            color: #0369a1;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
        }

        .nav-links .nav-btn {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .nav-links .nav-btn.btn-primary {
            background: white;
            color: #6366f1;
        }

        .nav-links .nav-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .nav-links .nav-btn.btn-primary:hover {
            background: #f8fafc;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">MOZCOMPRAS</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="<%= url('loja') %>" class="nav-btn">Ver Loja</a>
            <a href="/auth/access/login" class="nav-btn">Entrar</a>
            <a href="/new_user/register" class="nav-btn btn-primary">Começar Agora</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Transforme seu conhecimento em<br>lucro com a MOZCOMPRAS</h1>
        <p>A plataforma mais completa para vender e comprar infoprodutos em Moçambique.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center;">
            <a href="<%= url('loja') %>" class="cta-button">ACEDER À LOJA</a>
            <button class="cta-button"
                style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);"
                onclick="document.getElementById('registerModal').style.display = 'flex'">QUERO VENDER</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Facilidade de Venda</h3>
            <p>Cadastre seus produtos em minutos e comece a vender imediatamente usando M-Pesa e e-Mola.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Segurança Total</h3>
            <p>Seus pagamentos são processados com as tecnologias de segurança mais modernas do mercado.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Suporte 24/7</h3>
            <p>Nossa equipe está sempre disponível para ajudar você em cada passo da sua jornada.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Modal de Registo -->
    <div id="registerModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close" onclick="document.getElementById('registerModal').style.display='none'">&times;</span>
            <div class="registration-form">
                <h2>Crie sua conta</h2>
                <p class="info">
                    <strong>Informação:</strong> Após submeter o pedido, a sua conta será verificada e irá receber as
                    credenciais no email dentro de 24 horas.
                </p>
                <form onsubmit="handleMockRegister(event)">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Nome Completo</label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Seu nome" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>E-mail</label>
                        <input type="email" placeholder="seu@email.com" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Telefone</label>
                        <input type="tel" placeholder="Ex: 841234567" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit">Solicitar Acesso</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal de Login -->
    <div id="loginModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close" onclick="document.getElementById('loginModal').style.display='none'">&times;</span>
            <div class="registration-form">
                <h2>Entrar na Plataforma</h2>
                <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    Aceda ao seu painel de vendedor
                </p>
                <form onsubmit="handleMockLogin(event)">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>E-mail</label>
                        <input type="email" placeholder="seu@email.com" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Palavra-passe</label>
                        <input type="password" placeholder="••••••••" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit">Entrar</button>
                </form>
                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
                    Não tem conta? <a href="#"
                        onclick="event.preventDefault(); document.getElementById('loginModal').style.display='none'; document.getElementById('registerModal').style.display='flex';"
                        style="color: #6366f1; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">Registar agora</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const registerModal = document.getElementById("registerModal");
        const loginModal = document.getElementById("loginModal");

        const openRegister = document.getElementById("openRegister");
        const openLogin = document.getElementById("openLogin");

        if (openRegister) openRegister.onclick = () => registerModal.style.display = "flex";
        if (openLogin) openLogin.onclick = () => loginModal.style.display = "flex";

        window.onclick = function (event) {
            if (event.target == registerModal) registerModal.style.display = "none";
            if (event.target == loginModal) loginModal.style.display = "none";
        }

        function handleMockRegister(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            alert('Conta enviada para verificação! Irá receber as suas credenciais no email dentro de 24 horas.');
            registerModal.style.display = "none";
            e.target.reset();
        }

        function handleMockLogin(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            alert('Erro: Conta não encontrada.');
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>